n回頭是岸啊。。。"},{"pid":"a888b9c021bb175f11f00c746dcb52874d5a4384","tid":808233,"uid":105908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e368e164ce48aa34785ce9a0dab8bdae5877ddca","tid":808233,"uid":82651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c736b1085c5d96bf1047fe0ed214f9bb2ee04c08","tid":808233,"uid":105908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c723aecd8d4abbcf968537a39842b8171a11d751","tid":808233,"uid":82651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"巴打咁堅赫爾辛基渣上羅凡聶米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來回渣左二千幾km<br />\n事前book哂啲中間站hotel for休息<br />\n有啲係大city (tempere, oulu), 有啲完全係細town得間supermarket（不過都好夠野買）<br />\n除咗好攰之外都好玩既，一個既深刻既經歷<br />\n尤其係第一次渣雪地，淆到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"雪地渣車有咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:44:51.000Z","msg":"起步易磨呔，所以有啲人會教二波<br />\n起步<br />\n同埋之前我行高速好似右邊踩到冰定一大灘雪，之後skid哂爭啲炒，著哂abs，好彩最後拎得返堂呔無事<br />\n有時轉急彎時可能會輕微向外彎漂一漂<br />\n但基本上全程都係專心啲揸慢啲就冇咁危險（廢話）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但到咗一啲無人既大空地，又全部舖哂雪，你就可以為所欲為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09958aad491a5404b07072af1c40617f38c44a33","tid":808233,"uid":28332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:09:49.000Z","msg":"去過 冇揸車<br />\n搭內陸機飛去ivalo/roveniemi 就得 <br />\n價錢又唔貴"},{"pid":"818960e8aeaabb96e1a2a51d55b8572e3542c52b","tid":808233,"uid":97773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:24:07.000Z","msg":"無揸車去過inari，一行出酒店就見到極光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1580507e954d6dd947bce6bfbd1b30ead633411c","tid":808233,"uid":28332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"818960e8aeaabb96e1a2a51d55b8572e3542c52b","tid":808233,"uid":9